title: Crypto Whales Makes Over $3.3 Million Profit After $PEPE Price Surges over 1,300% in Six Months
description: The price of the meme-inspired cryptocurrency $PEPE has surged by more than 1,330% over the past six months, including a rise of over 800% in the last 30-day period, enough for a cryptocurrency whale to make over $3.3 million of profit off the cryptocurrency.
